0f3w. B\u0142\u0119dy w tre\u015bci mog\u0105 zaszkodzi\u0107 Twojej reputacji, wi\u0119c dbaj o poprawno\u015b\u0107 w tytu\u0142ach i punktach wypunktowanych.<\/li>\n<li><b>Testuj i analizuj<\/b>: Regularnie monitoruj wyniki swoich dzia\u0142a\u0144. Sprawdzaj, kt\u00f3re s\u0142owa kluczowe przyci\u0105gaj\u0105 najwi\u0119cej ruchu i dostosowuj strategi\u0119 w oparciu o zebrane dane.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Wykorzystanie b\u0142\u0119dnych pisowni i s\u0142\u00f3w kluczowych w alt text to sprytny spos\u00f3b na popraw\u0119 widoczno\u015bci Twoich produkt\u00f3w na Amazonie. Pami\u0119taj, aby zawsze dba\u0107 o jako\u015b\u0107 tre\u015bci, a wyniki mog\u0105 Ci\u0119 pozytywnie zaskoczy\u0107.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h1>Jak wykorzysta\u0107 b\u0142\u0119dne pisownie i s\u0142owa kluczowe na Amazonie?<\/h1>\n<p>Chcesz zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 widoczno<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":6816,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-6815","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-strategia"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6815"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=6815"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6815\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/6816"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.l